1.1 Basic
~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~

Use html5:

	<!DOCTYPE html>

Basic structure:

	<html lang="en">
	  <head>

	  </head>
	  <body>

	  </body>
	</html>

head used to include extern file and set page title.
body used to show page content.

Set encoding:

	<meta charset="UTF-8">

This is html comment:

	<!-- Hi, I'm comment! -->

Include extern css file:

	<link rel="stylesheet" href="/path/to/css">

Include extern javascript file:

	<script src="/path/to/js"></script>

Basic structure:

	<!DOCTYPE html>
	<html lang="en">
	<head>
	  <meta charset="UTF-8">
	  <title>This is title</title>
	  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/path/to/css">
	  <script src="/path/to/js"></script>
	</head>
	<body>
	  <!-- Comment Here -->
	  <p></p>

	  <h1></h1>
	  <h2></h2>
	  <h6></h6>

	  <ul>
	  	<li></li>
	  	<li></li>
	  	<li></li>
	  </ul>

	  <ol>
	  	<li></li>
	  	<li></li>
	  	<li></li>
	  </ol>

	  <table>
	  	<tr>
	  		<td></td>
	  	</tr>
	  </table>

	  <form action="" method="GET">

	  </form>

	  <form action="" method="POST">

	  </form>

	  <img src="" alt="">

	</body>
	</html>
